说梦话，<span class="_ _6"></span>举头一看，<span class="_ _6"></span>又见到万事万物</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y74 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">也是空的。<span class="_ _6"></span>同样，<span class="_ _a"></span>我过去说的话、<span class="_ _6"></span>做的事，<span class="_ _a"></span>似乎是真实不虚</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y75 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的，但实际上举头一看，也只不过是昨天的一场梦。 </div><div class="t m0 xc h4 y76 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这一点，<span class="_ _6"></span>每个人都需要明白。<span class="_ _a"></span>否则，<span class="_ _6"></span>你对感情、<span class="_ _a"></span>对生活</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
